# Recipe list – pagination, ordering, filtering (REST Client)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5100

### Default – first page, default pageSize (10), random shuffle
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes

### Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?page=2

### Custom pageSize
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?pageSize=5

### Same seed – deterministic order (same request twice = same order)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?seed=42

### Text search (query filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?query=taco

### Time range filter (min only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?minTime=20

### Time range filter (max only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?maxTime=45

### Time range filter (min and max)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?minTime=15&maxTime=60

### Category filter (include mode – recipes that have any of these categories)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?categoryIds=63108ec7425904cb101dc601&categoryMode=include

### Category filter (exclude mode – recipes that have none of these categories)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?categoryIds=63108ec7425904cb101dc601&categoryMode=exclude

### Ingredient filter (recipes that use any of these ingredients)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?ingredientIds=6310ad7242687f4a1cf7f226,6310ad7242687f4a1cf7f234

### Combined filters – query + time + category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?query=bean&minTime=10&maxTime=45&categoryIds=63108ec7425904cb101dc601

### Pagination with filters (page 2 of filtered results)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?query=chicken&page=2&pageSize=5

### Seed with filters (deterministic relevance order)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recipes?categoryIds=63108ec7425904cb101dc601&seed=123
